# tests/storage_smoke.ad
#
# F10-5 (#457) split: ahci/nvme/xhci L-shim exercises + cpio_capacity_smoke_test.
#
# Bodies were extracted verbatim from init/main.ad. The function
# definitions are unchanged; only their *location* has moved. boot
# orchestration in start_kernel() still calls each function by name
# at the same boot stage it always did, via re-import through
# tests/dispatcher.ad. See audit_F10_report.md F10-5.
#
# Imports below are the full import block from init/main.ad. Adder
# tolerates unused imports; the alternative (per-file minimised
# imports) would require auditing every call in 5k lines of moved
# bodies. The trade is: a wide import header on each split file in
# exchange for a clean, mechanically-verifiable extraction.

